# 🔄 Core Contract Lifecycle (FSM)

```text
DRAFT
  ↓ Submit for Review
UNDER_REVIEW
  ↓ Multi-Step Approval Complete
APPROVED
  ↓ Sign
SIGNED
  ↓ Activate
ACTIVE
  ↓ Expire / Terminate
EXPIRED / TERMINATED
```

