# 👥 Multi-Step Approval Workflow

## Approval Chain

```text
Vendor → Legal Manager → Finance → Admin
```

## 🚀 Features

### ✅ Sequential Approvals

Only the active approver can act.

### ✅ Approval Rounds

Supports rejection → edit → re-submit.

### ✅ Current Approval Step Tracking

System always knows:

```text
Who must approve next?
```

### ✅ Governance Enforcement

No skipping or bypassing.

